<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="entitle-vt">entitle <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'taɪtl/    美 /ɪn'taɪtl/  </p>
<p>[常用于被动语态]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>给...取名 / 命名：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She read a poem entitled"The Apple Tree".
她读了一首名为《苹果树》的诗。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>使...有权利 / 资格：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>entitle sb to (do) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are all entitled to equal protection under the law.
我们都有权受到法律的同等保护。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Her talent and experience entitled her <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the respect of her colleagues.  （2003 上海改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to  </p></div>